    <item>
      <title>普京在阅兵式上再次对西方发出核威胁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-09/putin-renews-nuclear-threats-against-west-in-victory-day-speech</link>
      <description><![CDATA[弗拉基米尔·普京总统在入侵乌克兰时警告西方不要威胁俄罗斯，并在莫斯科举行的纪念第二次世界大战胜利的年度阅兵式上再次炫耀核武力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-09/putin-renews-nuclear-threats-against-west-in-victory-day-speech</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 07:37:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>习近平誓言“永不忘记”后放弃访问被炸大使馆</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-09/xi-skips-visit-to-bombed-embassy-after-vowing-to-never-forget</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国家主席习近平似乎没有前往遭北约轰炸的中国前大使馆旧址就结束了对塞尔维亚的访问，因为他要在对美国为首的北约的谴责与处理与华盛顿的脆弱关系之间找到平衡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-09/xi-skips-visit-to-bombed-embassy-after-vowing-to-never-forget</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 05:21:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
